{"version":1,"cues":[{"start":1,"end":7.426,"text":"好！我们来添加你的第一台服务器。两条命令，大约一分钟就能搞定。","words":[{"start":1,"end":7.426,"char":[0,31]}]},{"start":8.208,"end":11.347,"text":"整套架构由两部分组成。命令行工具装在你的笔记本上，服务器上则运行一个叫做","words":[{"start":8.208,"end":11.347,"char":[0,36]}]},{"start":11.347,"end":14.486,"text":"renet","words":[{"start":11.347,"end":14.486,"char":[0,5]}]},{"start":14.486,"end":17.625,"text":"的编排器。CLI","words":[{"start":14.486,"end":17.625,"char":[0,8]}]},{"start":17.625,"end":20.764,"text":"通过","words":[{"start":17.625,"end":20.764,"char":[0,2]}]},{"start":20.764,"end":23.903,"text":"SSH","words":[{"start":20.764,"end":23.903,"char":[0,3]}]},{"start":23.903,"end":27.042,"text":"连接服务器，所以你永远不需要手动登录服务器。","words":[{"start":23.903,"end":27.042,"char":[0,22]}]},{"start":30.316,"end":34.008,"text":"首先，让我们创建一个配置文件。该文件将保存","words":[{"start":30.316,"end":34.008,"char":[0,21]}]},{"start":34.008,"end":37.7,"text":"SSH","words":[{"start":34.008,"end":37.7,"char":[0,3]}]},{"start":37.7,"end":41.392,"text":"密钥、机器列表以及后续所有操作的基础设施配置。","words":[{"start":37.7,"end":41.392,"char":[0,23]}]},{"start":42.642,"end":48.128,"text":"配置已创建。后续所有设置都保存在这一个文件里。","words":[{"start":42.642,"end":48.128,"char":[0,23]}]},{"start":51.445,"end":54.495,"text":"现在让我们从命令行注册服务器，提供其名称、IP","words":[{"start":51.445,"end":54.495,"char":[0,23]}]},{"start":54.495,"end":57.545,"text":"地址和","words":[{"start":54.495,"end":57.545,"char":[0,3]}]},{"start":57.545,"end":60.594,"text":"SSH","words":[{"start":57.545,"end":60.594,"char":[0,3]}]},{"start":60.594,"end":63.644,"text":"用户名。主机密钥会自动扫描以建立信任连接。","words":[{"start":60.594,"end":63.644,"char":[0,21]}]},{"start":63.644,"end":66.805,"text":"服务器已注册。主机密钥已自动扫描。","words":[{"start":63.644,"end":66.805,"char":[0,17]}]},{"start":70.069,"end":73.099,"text":"接下来让我们配置服务器。这一步会安装","words":[{"start":70.069,"end":73.099,"char":[0,18]}]},{"start":73.099,"end":76.129,"text":"renet","words":[{"start":73.099,"end":76.129,"char":[0,5]}]},{"start":76.129,"end":79.16,"text":"并创建加密数据存储。完成后，服务器就可以托管仓库了。","words":[{"start":76.129,"end":79.16,"char":[0,26]}]},{"start":79.16,"end":82.947,"text":"完成。renet 已安装，数据存储已就绪。","words":[{"start":79.16,"end":81.053,"char":[0,8]},{"start":81.053,"end":82.947,"char":[9,21]}]},{"start":83.72,"end":87.116,"text":"添加服务器就到这里！下个教程见。","words":[{"start":83.72,"end":87.116,"char":[0,16]}]}]}